description:
This is the additional puzzle pack for "Jigsaw Masterpieces". The following 10 puzzle images are included.
-Apple Pie / USA
-Panna Cotta / Italy
-Creme Brulee / France
-Nanaimo Bars / Canada
-Belgian Waffle / Belgium
-Wagashi / Japan
-Lamington / Australia
-Banoffee Pie / United Kingdom
-Brigadeiro / Brazil
-Tarta de Santiago / Spain
name: Desserts from Around the World
